snippet.title: Trail of Ayash Trailer
snippet.description:
Unreal Engine 4 In-Game Engine Render (Sequencer)
Website - http://trailofayash.com
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/trail_of_ayash/
ArtStation - https://www.artstation.com/trail_of_ayash

Trail of Ayash is an innovative and exciting open world game focused on the various indigenous people, and their struggles. Our world is a unique version of the lands dominated by the myths and legends of Its Inhabitants. Various tribes interact with one another, engaging in diplomacy, war, and expansion. This game is not historically related and doesn't include any real tribe.

Music used: Alexandr Zhelanov
